                            <comment id="12500258" author="jimk" created="Wed, 30 May 2007 23:11:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merge takes far too long to execute over a single RPC. Further if you want to compact the META table, the HBase instance should not even be on-line. Merge will be an inherently off-line operation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
