                            <comment id="12501008" author="jimk" created="Sun, 3 Jun 2007 08:58:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes for part 2: merge:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MiniHBaseCluster&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add constructor so the mini HBase cluster can be started on a&lt;br/&gt;
  running HDFS cluster. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;AbstractMergeTestBase, TestMergeMeta, TestMergeTable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;new test case for table merging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HClient&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;checkMaster throws MasterNotRunningException&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add isMasterRunning&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;removed empty mergeRegions method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HMaster&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;moved bootstrap region creation (createNewHRegion, addRegionToMeta)&lt;br/&gt;
  to HRegion &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;removed empty mergeRegions method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HMasterInterface&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;removed mergeRegions method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HMerge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;new module. Implements merge as a client side operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HRegion&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;moved createNewHRegion, addRegionInfoToMeta from HMaster to here&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;added method largestHStore, used by merge to determine if two&lt;br/&gt;
  regions should be merged.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;HRegionInfo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;now implements WritableComparable instead of just Writable&lt;/li&gt;
